&lt;p&gt;Aerospike is the real-time database for mission-critical use cases and workloads, including machine learning, generative, and agentic AI. Aerospike powers millions of transactions per second with millisecond latency, at a fraction of the total cost of ownership compared to other databases.&amp;nbsp;Global leaders, including&amp;nbsp;Adobe, Airtel, Barclays, Criteo, DBS Bank, Experian, Grab, HDFC Bank, PayPal, Sony Interactive Entertainment, The Trade Desk, and Wayfair,&amp;nbsp;rely on Aerospike for&amp;nbsp;customer 360, fraud detection, real-time bidding,&amp;nbsp;profile stores, recommendation engines,&amp;nbsp;and other use cases.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;At Aerospike, we dream big and deliver even bigger. Our mission is to&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;unleash the power of the world’s real-time data&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;with a database built for&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;infinite scale, speed, and sustainability&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To foster strong team alignment and productivity, Bay Area–based team members are expected to work from the office 3 times per week—typically Tuesday through Thursday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re ready to shape the future of data, join us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;As our company scales, our financial infrastructure and strategic planning must keep pace. We are looking for a proactive, detail-oriented &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;139&quot;&gt;Finance Intern&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team for Summer 2026. In this role, you won&#39;t just be crunching numbers in a silo—you will be an active contributor to our financial operations, helping ensure our leadership team has the insights and data they need to drive the business forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;This internship offers a deep dive into modern corporate finance. You’ll gain hands-on experience in financial planning, data automation, and SaaS metrics while working directly with cutting-edge finance technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;9&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Financial Reporting &amp;amp; Presentations:&lt;/strong&gt; Assist in preparing management presentations, monthly financial reviews, and reports for senior leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Billing &amp;amp; Revenue Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Support usage-based billing analysis and automation initiatives. This includes exploring complex billing data, identifying discrepancies, and helping develop scalable tools to improve accuracy and operational efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;System &amp;amp; Data Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Engage with FP&amp;amp;A and Business Intelligence (BI) software for report creation, financial analysis, and data maintenance to ensure absolute reliability in our reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Finance Transformation:&lt;/strong&gt; Support process modernization initiatives, including exploring and implementing AI-enabled tools and automated finance workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 data-path-to-node=&quot;11&quot;&g

&lt;p&gt;Aerospike is the&amp;nbsp;real-time database&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;mission-critical use cases and workloads, including&amp;nbsp;machine learning, generative, and agentic AI.&amp;nbsp;Aerospike powers millions of transactions per second with millisecond latency, at a fraction of the total cost of ownership compared to other databases.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Global leaders, including&amp;nbsp;Adobe, Airtel, Barclays, Criteo, DBS Bank, Experian, Grab, HDFC Bank, PayPal, Sony Interactive Entertainment, The Trade Desk, and Wayfair,&amp;nbsp;rely on Aerospike for&amp;nbsp;customer 360, fraud detection, real-time bidding,&amp;nbsp;profile stores, recommendation engines,&amp;nbsp;and other use cases.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;At Aerospike, we dream big and deliver even bigger. Our mission is to &lt;strong&gt;unleash the power of the world’s real-time data&lt;/strong&gt; with a database built for &lt;strong&gt;infinite scale, speed, and sustainability&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To foster strong team alignment and productivity, Bay Area–based team members are expected to work from the office 3 times per week—typically Tuesday through Thursday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re ready to shape the future of data, join us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Aerospike operates with staff working in-office and remotely across multiple countries, and IT is&amp;nbsp;what keeps every function running without friction. We&#39;re hiring a Head of IT to lead the function&amp;nbsp;end to end: ownership of the architecture decisions behind the systems the company runs on,&amp;nbsp;and hands-on leadership of day-to-day operations and helpdesk. This person leads a team that&amp;nbsp;will scale with the business, sets IT priorities, and reports on them directly to executive leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
