&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;IT Operations and Helpdesk&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;● Own IT helpdesk operations, including ticket queue management, response time targets,&amp;nbsp;and escalation paths&lt;br&gt;● Own employee onboarding and offboarding logistics, including hardware provisioning,&amp;nbsp;account setup, and access deprovisioning, in partnership with People Ops&lt;br&gt;● Own endpoint hardware lifecycle management, including procurement, deployment, and&amp;nbsp;refresh cycles&lt;br&gt;● Coordinate with Security &amp;amp; Compliance on endpoint security tooling and identity and&amp;nbsp;access management, ensuring IT operations align with security policy&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Leadership and Cross-Functional Planning&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;● Manage a team of 2-3 IT professionals, with a hiring plan tied to company growth&lt;br&gt;● Set IT support standards and service level targets&lt;br&gt;● Own IT governance practices for company systems, including access review cadence&amp;nbsp;and system audit readiness&lt;br&gt;● Own the IT budget and prioritize spend against operational need&lt;br&gt;● Serve as the IT lead on cross-functional initiatives&lt;br&gt;● Partner with People Ops on IT components of office moves and expansions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Requirements&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;● 8-12 years in IT roles, including 3-5 years managing a team&lt;br&gt;● Experience owning IT architecture decisions for business-critical systems&lt;br&gt;● Direct experience running a helpdesk function at a company of comparable

