&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Aerospike EMEA is in a strong growth phase, and we’re building for scale. We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Account Executive &lt;/strong&gt;who wants to have real ownership, real impact, and the opportunity to help shape how we partner with high-growth, technology-forward Digital Native customers across the region. A true sales leader who can both expand existing relationships and secure new logo business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
