&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is not a “run-the-book” role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is about leading, expanding, and winning within strategic, innovative fast growing accounts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
