&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source, develop, and close new business opportunities to consistently exceed quarterly sales targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a deep understanding of Aerospike’s products, value proposition, and competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute effective territory planning and account management strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively engage target prospects and evangelize Aerospike solutions and customer success stories with Development leaders and technical teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver compelling presentations using industry knowledge, market trends, and customer case studies to clearly articulate Aerospike’s value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify, document, and manage all opportunities within Salesforce (SFDC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute sales strategies in a fast-paced, small-team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide the highest level of customer service and act as a trusted advisor to customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to broader sales strategy and share best practices and success stories with peers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend and support regional events, meetups, and customer-facing activities&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
