&lt;li&gt;Located in the United States with strong preference for Austin, San Francisco/San Jose Bay Area, or New York&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong foundational understanding of database technologies and data platforms&lt;/li&gt;
