&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Own and grow a portfolio of &lt;strong&gt;named strategic Digital Native customers in Israel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Drive expansions, upsell renewals,and cross-sell within complex top notch digital natives accounts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
