&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simplify relentlessly.&lt;/strong&gt; You are building something that has not been built before. You invent the patterns, then strip out steps: automate the manual, delete the unnecessary, and find the simplest design that delivers the outcome.&lt;/li&gt;
