&lt;li&gt;Develop high-performance, low-latency code for interacting with storage and network hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Debug and optimize OS-level issues across Linux-based environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure system quality through rigorous testing and benchmarking.&lt;/li&gt;
